view over the fjords and Drangey island. It has a hot swimming pool, a hot tub, very clean showers, and lockers and all for just 900 ISK ($8).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Good to know:<\/strong> The camping is just a 3-minute walk from the pool!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/iceland\/campsites-iceland\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Best Campsites in Iceland<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153228\/campsites-iceland-infinity-pool-hofsos.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"294\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8035\" class=\"wp-image-8035 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153228\/campsites-iceland-infinity-pool-hofsos.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153228\/campsites-iceland-infinity-pool-hofsos-300x196.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23153228\/campsites-iceland-infinity-pool-hofsos-600x393.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upl